02:11:10,228 --> 02:11:23,888
v ip 2 1. e u. or g

1447
02:11:25,895 --> 02:11:30,508
<i>"Liputan Hinzpeter yang diliputnya
dengan bertaruh nyawa,"</i>

1448
02:11:30,628 --> 02:11:34,375
<i>"dengan bantuan Kim Sa-Bok,
ditayangkan ke seluruh dunia"</i>

1449
02:11:34,495 --> 02:11:37,962
<i>"Ini membongkar tekanan
diktator militer"</i>

1450
02:11:38,228 --> 02:11:41,708
<i>"Hinzpeter mencoba beberapa kali
mencari supir taksi, Kim Sa-Bok"</i>

1451
02:11:41,842 --> 02:11:43,642
<i>"Di Januari 2016,
dia meninggal dunia"</i>

1452
02:11:43,762 --> 02:11:45,922
<i>"tanpa bertemu dengannya lagi"</i>

1453
02:11:50,762 --> 02:11:54,862
<i>"Mendiang Jurgen Hinzpeter,
November 2015, di Ratzeburg"</i>

1454
02:11:55,482 --> 02:11:59,402
Akan sangat menyenangkan

1455
02:11:59,482 --> 02:12:03,922
